title: Large 2 Bedroom Ready For Tour Today!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Evergreen Ridge Apartments.', 'Looking for a new place to call home?', 'Come take a look at our large 2 bedroom 2 bath apartment home which features private balcony, lots of windows which provide plenty of natural light, open kitchen, and huge primary bedroom.', "Don't miss it.", 'Our apartment homes feature:', 'Spacious Floor Plans', 'Spectacular Views on some Top Floors', 'All Electric Kitchen', 'Spacious Closets', 'Private Decks/Patios', 'Carpet and Wood Laminate Flooring', 'High Speed Internet Ready', 'Assigned and Covered Parking', 'Explore the Area:', 'Seafood City Supermarket 0.9 mile', 'Milagra Ridge Golden Gate', 'National Recreation Area 1 mile', 'Southwood Shopping Center', '3.0 miles', 'Serramonte Shopping Center 3.1 miles', 'Costco Wholesale 3.5 miles', 'San Bruno Bart Station', '3.8 miles', 'Pacifica State Beach 5.2 miles', 'San Francisco International Airport 5.5 miles', 'Office Hours Monday - Saturday 9 am to 6 pm', 'Tours Until 5:30 pm', 'Located in San Bruno, San Mateo County.', 'Near South San Francisco', 'Prices, availability, and terms are subject to change without notice and subject to approval of application and credit.', 'Pet restrictions: size and breed; additional security deposit; monthly pet rent']
